	bool "Mediatek Embedded Technology"
	depends on FTRACE && TRACING
	help
	  For Mediatek Embedded Technology features.
	  It depends on FTRACE and TRACING.
	  Select "Y" if you want to use.
	  Select "N" if you are not sure.

